  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the effects of tegaserod on orocecal and colonic transit in patients
      over 65 years with chronic constipation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    Terminated early due to regulatory action suspending tegaserod use in 2007
  </why_stopped>
